OOC: I am so sorry for my short departure. One of my family members has 
dominated my computer for the past two days and I was unable to participate 
in the RPG. But, now Im back.

::: HELL BEAST looks to RAMPAGE ::: Rampage, I do suppose you are right. We 
need some R and R before another long and almost pointless battle.

::: He sits in the command chair and reads a dat on the status of the other 
fractions, giving command to Rampage for the moment. :::

~~~~~~~~

::: TRANSANULAS, who had recived the transmission from the Oblitercons, now 
responds in the secrecy of the lab :::

::: TRANSANULAS ::: Ah, Excellent Dark One! I need you to escourt my 
associate, Quickstrike, to a secure location. Im sure he can figure out 
somewhere...prehaps his friend Rowdy Wolf or something. He is damaged so I 
hope you do have some kind of medical training. His coordinates are at 
6.99-4. Please hurry. Your blank Proto-form awaits you.

::: The transmission ends and the spider turns to look at the stasis pod 
glimmering in the light. He can just make out the blank face of the being 
inside. ...Transanulas mused at what the Oblitercons would use it for. :::

~~~~~~~~

::: OMINOUS PRIME looked at Quickstrike from atop a tree branch. He was 
waiting for the Oblitercons. At last he might find some bots who were his 
equals, and a true fraction that understood his belives. All he could do now 
was wait. ::::
